WEBVTT


00:00:11.529 --> 00:00:17.184
(Beiyan Police Station)

00:00:23.622 --> 00:00:24.572
(Termination of Residential Surveillance)

00:00:24.572 --> 00:00:26.862
(On July 15, 2011, Meng Guangcai
was put under residential surveillance.)

00:00:26.862 --> 00:00:28.096
(Due to insufficient evidence,
surveillance is now terminated.)

00:00:55.020 --> 00:00:56.200
Eighteen years.

00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:58.740
It's been eighteen years.

00:00:59.240 --> 00:01:01.740
The only blood sample
from the 6.10 case.

00:01:02.420 --> 00:01:06.060
We brought Meng Guangcai in
because of this blood sample.

00:01:07.060 --> 00:01:09.560
We hoped to find the owner
of the blood sample

00:01:09.560 --> 00:01:10.840
to bring down Meng Guangcai.

00:01:11.239 --> 00:01:14.159
But then, this person surfaced

00:01:15.780 --> 00:01:16.980
and died before our eyes.

00:01:17.859 --> 00:01:19.719
The person at the cemetery
was Huang Mantang.

00:01:21.140 --> 00:01:22.920
The person in the hospital
is Xue Yonghui.

00:01:23.400 --> 00:01:25.299
We've got all the information.

00:01:25.299 --> 00:01:27.060
All the testimonies match up.

00:01:27.060 --> 00:01:31.200
But there's not a shred of evidence
that points to Meng Guangcai.

00:02:40.768 --> 00:02:43.604
=The Silent Rift=

00:02:43.774 --> 00:02:46.819
=Episode 15=
(The Truth?)

00:02:47.180 --> 00:02:50.120
Today, Meng Guangcai,
Caisheng Group's chairman,

00:02:50.180 --> 00:02:51.919
was released
from residential surveillance

00:02:52.060 --> 00:02:54.620
I'm He Huan, reporting live for you.

00:02:57.180 --> 00:02:58.270
- They're here.
- Hello.

00:02:58.656 --> 00:02:59.520
May I interview you?

00:02:59.580 --> 00:03:00.740
Hello, may I interview you?

00:03:01.139 --> 00:03:01.840
Stop filming.

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:02.460
- Ms. Xue.
- Ms. Xue.

00:03:02.639 --> 00:03:03.699
No photos, please.

00:03:03.900 --> 00:03:04.780
- Say something.
- No interviews.

00:03:04.780 --> 00:03:05.960
- It's fine.
- No interviews.

00:03:06.240 --> 00:03:07.740
- Make way.
- Could you comment?

00:03:07.740 --> 00:03:08.460
- No interviews.
- Say something.

00:03:23.800 --> 00:03:26.020
Rules say
I shouldn't be here seeing you off.

00:03:27.080 --> 00:03:28.800
But we're old acquaintances after all.

00:03:30.780 --> 00:03:31.960
You'll leave here today.

00:03:32.500 --> 00:03:33.500
So I came to see you.

00:03:44.180 --> 00:03:45.800
Got something to say to me, don't you?

00:03:48.900 --> 00:03:50.080
You've got luck on your side.

00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:54.740
Zhu,

00:03:56.460 --> 00:03:58.120
we've known each other for 28 years

00:03:59.620 --> 00:04:01.060
and been at odds for nearly twenty.

00:04:04.240 --> 00:04:05.560
What luck do I have?

00:04:09.199 --> 00:04:12.520
I, Meng Guangcai,
am destined to rot in the dirt.

00:04:15.199 --> 00:04:17.579
From the day you came in, we all knew

00:04:19.279 --> 00:04:20.860
you were involved in that robbery.

00:04:22.300 --> 00:04:24.180
We just lack direct evidence
against you.

00:04:25.420 --> 00:04:26.519
This time, you won.

00:04:28.360 --> 00:04:32.000
(Termination of Residential Surveillance)
You can leave here today.

00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:42.060
I spent half my life climbing,

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:47.060
almost touching the clouds above.

00:04:48.819 --> 00:04:52.939
Then you yanked me down midair.

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:56.560
You say I won?

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:02.600
You told me Meng Xiaoliang isn't my son,

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:07.540
ripping open that wound in my heart

00:05:10.420 --> 00:05:12.160
and making me watch it bleed again.

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:16.500
Did I win?

00:05:20.259 --> 00:05:23.600
Lijun, Dazhu, and Yonghui.

00:05:24.379 --> 00:05:26.620
You've caught them all, one by one.

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:33.740
And you say I won?

00:05:36.220 --> 00:05:38.240
- Step back. Step back.
- Mom, let's wait in the car.

00:05:38.439 --> 00:05:39.120
We'll wait here.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.420
Get back. Stop filming! Stop it!

00:05:40.420 --> 00:05:43.319
Your father will see us
the moment he steps out.

00:05:48.259 --> 00:05:49.879
To protect your secrets

00:05:50.379 --> 00:05:52.060
and to grasp your clouds,

00:05:53.439 --> 00:05:55.180
do you know how many people
got implicated?

00:05:55.560 --> 00:05:57.420
Do you realize how many people
you've affected?

00:05:57.500 --> 00:06:00.620
Weren't they yanked from the sky too?

00:06:00.740 --> 00:06:03.259
Don't their hearts bleed just as much?

00:06:03.259 --> 00:06:04.439
Meng Guangcai, listen up.

00:06:04.759 --> 00:06:07.680
My whole life is tied to yours.

00:06:07.680 --> 00:06:08.500
I swear,

00:06:09.259 --> 00:06:10.319
with a task force or not,

00:06:10.319 --> 00:06:12.120
no matter what I do, I'll hunt you down.

00:06:12.120 --> 00:06:13.660
My fate is tied to yours.

00:06:13.660 --> 00:06:16.240
The 6.10 case will definitely be solved.

00:06:50.439 --> 00:06:51.439
I came today

00:06:54.879 --> 00:06:56.180
to tell you one thing.

00:06:59.060 --> 00:07:00.180
You've won this time.

00:07:10.040 --> 00:07:10.980
You can leave now.

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:17.180
Zhu,

00:07:22.300 --> 00:07:23.300
I'm not leaving.

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:32.420
What are you saying?

00:07:34.100 --> 00:07:35.439
Today, I'll let you win.

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:44.680
Tell me.

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:53.379
Where could I possibly go?

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:07.060
Mr. Chen raised me.

00:08:08.300 --> 00:08:09.879
His eyes were like that.

00:08:10.980 --> 00:08:15.060
If you were me, could you ignore it?

00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:18.560
Meng Xiaoliang

00:08:19.879 --> 00:08:20.800
is my son.

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:25.819
I needed money to buy his life.

00:08:26.740 --> 00:08:29.000
If it were you,
what would you have done?

00:08:31.767 --> 00:08:37.259
(Beiyan County Hospital, 1993)

00:08:38.820 --> 00:08:40.259
Your son has limited mobility.

00:08:40.259 --> 00:08:42.259
He's weaker than most children.

00:08:42.820 --> 00:08:44.639
As parents, you must be extra careful.

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:47.259
Don't rush to discharge him now.

00:08:47.500 --> 00:08:48.860
His fever has broken.

00:08:49.159 --> 00:08:51.480
If he starts coughing again,
call me immediately.

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:52.620
Okay, Doctor.

00:08:52.620 --> 00:08:53.639
Thank you, Doctor.

00:08:58.220 --> 00:09:01.460
You do care about your mom, kiddo.

00:09:02.379 --> 00:09:04.519
It's uncomfortable
at the construction site.

00:09:04.820 --> 00:09:06.940
So she can stay here
a few more days, right?

00:09:07.379 --> 00:09:10.139
Hospital costs drain money like water.

00:09:12.240 --> 00:09:14.879
Don't worry about the money.

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:16.080
Stop overthinking it.

00:09:16.740 --> 00:09:18.000
I'm heading out for a bit.

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:19.220
I'll be back later.

00:09:20.500 --> 00:09:24.259
Dazhu told me you're helping
other foremen collect the overdue wages.

00:09:25.720 --> 00:09:26.820
Hanging firecrackers again?

00:09:30.120 --> 00:09:31.700
What firecrackers?

00:09:33.259 --> 00:09:35.120
But that firecracker thing last time

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:37.259
actually made me famous.

00:09:37.580 --> 00:09:38.940
So other workers came to me.

00:09:38.940 --> 00:09:41.000
They couldn't get their money
from other sites

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:42.440
and asked me to help.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:47.000
Don't worry. I have you guys now.

00:09:47.139 --> 00:09:48.340
I won't do anything reckless.

00:09:50.740 --> 00:09:52.240
We dragged you down.

00:09:53.580 --> 00:09:55.379
Otherwise, you wouldn't be doing that.

00:09:56.139 --> 00:09:58.220
Stop overthinking and talking nonsense.

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:04.440
Raising our son healthy
is a huge achievement.

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:06.460
I'll go now. Be back later.

00:10:07.259 --> 00:10:08.139
- Okay?
- Go ahead.

00:10:09.740 --> 00:10:10.960
(Ward)
I'll be back later.

00:10:12.160 --> 00:10:18.360
(Beiyan Shaliang Rural Credit Union)

00:10:18.360 --> 00:10:19.360
It's only five yuan left.

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:21.320
You sure you don't want
to clear it out and close?

00:10:24.620 --> 00:10:25.360
Next, please.

00:10:29.940 --> 00:10:31.220
The test results are back.

00:10:31.779 --> 00:10:33.960
It's an atrioventricular septal defect.

00:10:34.259 --> 00:10:36.120
It's congenital. He needs surgery soon.

00:10:36.120 --> 00:10:38.200
Doctor, wasn't it just a cough?

00:10:38.259 --> 00:10:39.620
How'd he get heart disease?

00:10:40.080 --> 00:10:42.879
Doctor, roughly how much
will this surgery cost?

00:10:43.379 --> 00:10:45.200
It depends on the case.

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:51.139
Generally, for such surgery,
prepare at least 20,000 yuan upfront.

00:10:54.460 --> 00:10:55.500
20,000 yuan?

00:10:55.740 --> 00:10:56.320
Yes.

00:10:56.460 --> 00:10:58.820
I thought he could be discharged
after the tests?

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:00.860
He can't be discharged yet.

00:11:01.460 --> 00:11:03.039
The previous fever and cough

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:05.039
suggested a lung vascular infection

00:11:05.039 --> 00:11:06.460
caused by congestive heart failure.

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:10.039
It's a classic sign
of congenital heart defect

00:11:10.039 --> 00:11:11.440
manifesting externally.

00:11:12.740 --> 00:11:14.720
We were only suspicious before.

00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:17.120
That's why we
did the external tests on him

00:11:18.139 --> 00:11:19.980
to confirm it.

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:22.120
Then, Doctor,
when will the surgery happen?

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:25.080
And when do we need
to pay the surgery fee?

00:11:25.200 --> 00:11:26.460
The sooner, the better.

00:11:26.580 --> 00:11:28.539
The longer it's delayed,
the worse it is for him,

00:11:29.159 --> 00:11:31.279
and the risk of surgical failure
also increases.

00:11:32.639 --> 00:11:34.500
If we don't do this surgery,

00:11:35.500 --> 00:11:37.120
what's the worst possible outcome?

00:11:37.360 --> 00:11:38.240
It's very serious.

00:12:02.860 --> 00:12:04.000
Don't panic too much.

00:12:04.740 --> 00:12:06.080
Xiaoliang is our son.

00:12:07.440 --> 00:12:10.940
I'd give my life to save him.

00:12:21.480 --> 00:12:23.860
I'll go ask the doctor
to look at his lab report.

00:12:45.620 --> 00:12:46.480
Lower it. Slower.

00:12:46.500 --> 00:12:47.039
Got it.

00:12:47.720 --> 00:12:48.240
Take it slow.

00:12:48.240 --> 00:12:49.080
Okay.

00:12:52.000 --> 00:12:55.500
Guangcai, if it comes to it,
maybe tell Zhu

00:12:55.639 --> 00:12:57.080
and ask him for help.

00:12:58.139 --> 00:12:59.120
We owe him too much.

00:12:59.659 --> 00:13:01.039
I really don't know how to ask.

00:13:01.779 --> 00:13:05.120
And 20,000 is a huge amount.

00:13:05.139 --> 00:13:06.080
Watch out.

00:13:06.080 --> 00:13:07.080
He might not have a way.

00:13:08.200 --> 00:13:09.620
Let's just see how it goes.

00:13:10.759 --> 00:13:14.820
By the way, Dazhu, go look around.

00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:16.820
See if there are any odd jobs.

00:13:17.620 --> 00:13:20.620
Preferably the kind
that pays daily, got it?

00:13:21.399 --> 00:13:22.399
Wait, let me do it first.

00:13:23.899 --> 00:13:24.768
Come here.

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:30.620
Otherwise, we can't afford
Xiaoliang's hospital stay.

00:13:31.200 --> 00:13:34.879
Alright, I'll go to the market
and ask after finishing this job.

00:13:36.440 --> 00:13:37.240
Guangcai.

00:13:39.860 --> 00:13:40.639
Guangcai.

00:13:43.580 --> 00:13:46.460
Guangcai, Lijun told us about your kid.

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:48.460
You've always looked out
for us brothers.

00:13:48.940 --> 00:13:50.960
Now you're in trouble.
We brothers must help.

00:13:51.740 --> 00:13:53.720
It's not much. We brothers chipped in.

00:13:53.720 --> 00:13:54.759
Please take it, Guangcai.

00:13:57.360 --> 00:13:58.740
- Take it, Guangcai.
- Take it, Guangcai.

00:13:58.740 --> 00:13:59.960
- It's not much.
- We chipped in.

00:13:59.960 --> 00:14:00.539
Accept it.

00:14:01.080 --> 00:14:01.820
Guangcai.

00:14:02.460 --> 00:14:05.080
Others are chipping in too.

00:14:05.080 --> 00:14:06.120
It's coming right over.

00:14:06.639 --> 00:14:07.720
We also agreed

00:14:07.860 --> 00:14:10.820
we'll all donate today's wages
for the kid's treatment.

00:14:17.500 --> 00:14:18.639
Th-thank you.

00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:22.820
Guangcai,

00:14:23.860 --> 00:14:25.000
look who's here.

00:14:31.320 --> 00:14:32.379
Thank you all.

00:14:33.080 --> 00:14:34.080
I'll go over there.

00:14:38.500 --> 00:14:39.940
I'll thank you all for Guangcai.

00:14:39.980 --> 00:14:40.720
Thank you all.

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:41.720
Okay. No problem.

00:14:41.840 --> 00:14:42.820
Let's go. Back to work.

00:14:42.820 --> 00:14:43.552
Go.

00:14:48.736 --> 00:14:49.620
Alright.

00:14:56.820 --> 00:14:58.432
Principal Chen said not to tell you.

00:14:59.080 --> 00:15:00.639
The doctor said it's just a bruise.

00:15:01.360 --> 00:15:03.139
But his cataract surgery can't wait.

00:15:03.139 --> 00:15:04.940
If it's delayed any further,
he'll go blind.

00:15:11.080 --> 00:15:12.879
Principal Chen
needs someone to care for him.

00:15:14.259 --> 00:15:15.320
You go back first.

00:15:16.200 --> 00:15:17.840
I'll figure out the rest.

00:15:21.820 --> 00:15:24.240
Guangcai, I heard about Xiaoliang.

00:15:24.740 --> 00:15:25.820
I want to drop out.

00:15:30.240 --> 00:15:31.259
What nonsense is that?

00:15:32.460 --> 00:15:33.840
You'll have Gaokao soon.

00:15:35.039 --> 00:15:36.320
If you don't study, then what?

00:15:36.960 --> 00:15:38.500
To work with you guys on site.

00:15:38.639 --> 00:15:39.840
Guangcai, I'm strong, look.

00:15:41.700 --> 00:15:43.039
What's the use in you doing this?

00:15:43.340 --> 00:15:44.539
There's no future in this.

00:15:55.580 --> 00:15:57.039
Us suffering is fine.

00:15:57.740 --> 00:15:58.820
But you can't suffer.

00:15:59.039 --> 00:16:00.539
What does Qin always tell you?

00:16:00.539 --> 00:16:01.259
Forgot all of it?

00:16:01.259 --> 00:16:03.000
Guangcai, Qin gave up studying for me.

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:03.580
So can I.

00:16:03.580 --> 00:16:05.000
What's a little hardship?

00:16:05.000 --> 00:16:07.500
Listen to me. Once you get into college,

00:16:08.039 --> 00:16:09.860
become a lawyer, a teacher,

00:16:09.860 --> 00:16:11.500
or an accountant, and make it,

00:16:11.820 --> 00:16:13.259
then you can truly help Qin.

00:16:13.259 --> 00:16:14.379
Do you have to be like me,

00:16:14.379 --> 00:16:16.960
working as a laborer
on construction sites

00:16:16.960 --> 00:16:18.000
and being a pauper?

00:16:18.120 --> 00:16:19.320
What can a pauper help with?

00:16:19.700 --> 00:16:21.240
Do we need another pauper?

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:37.200
Listen to me.

00:16:38.840 --> 00:16:40.120
Go inside and have a drink.

00:16:41.220 --> 00:16:41.820
Wash your face.

00:16:41.960 --> 00:16:43.360
Later, I'll take you to see Qin.

00:16:45.120 --> 00:16:46.460
Cheer up.

00:16:46.960 --> 00:16:48.240
Chin up, young man.

00:16:49.240 --> 00:16:50.620
Go on.

00:16:51.240 --> 00:16:51.879
Go.

00:16:53.360 --> 00:16:54.000
Go.

00:17:43.660 --> 00:17:44.680
You have no idea

00:17:46.539 --> 00:17:49.519
how much I hated myself back then.

00:17:52.160 --> 00:17:54.299
I hate myself for being useless waste.

00:17:55.480 --> 00:17:57.819
I couldn't even save my own loved ones.

00:17:58.640 --> 00:17:59.700
You had a choice.

00:17:59.700 --> 00:18:00.660
Why commit crimes?

00:18:00.660 --> 00:18:01.980
I must save them.

00:18:12.900 --> 00:18:13.500
Come on.

00:18:22.304 --> 00:18:22.960
Give it to me.

00:18:25.420 --> 00:18:28.339
Guangcai, the pay here is way too low.

00:18:28.640 --> 00:18:31.039
Even if the three of us
work nonstop 24 hours,

00:18:31.039 --> 00:18:32.960
it still won't cover the hospital bills.

00:18:36.099 --> 00:18:37.480
I want to go back to Magou.

00:18:37.940 --> 00:18:39.519
Mr. Chen is all alone there.

00:18:39.519 --> 00:18:41.180
I'm really worried.

00:18:42.299 --> 00:18:45.299
You going back won't solve anything.

00:18:46.440 --> 00:18:49.779
Here's what we'll do.
I'll send Lijun back tomorrow

00:18:49.900 --> 00:18:50.799
to check on things.

00:18:51.539 --> 00:18:52.660
You just stay out of it.

00:18:54.140 --> 00:18:55.960
Make sure that side is tied down tight.

00:18:56.380 --> 00:18:56.992
Okay.

00:19:00.420 --> 00:19:01.480
Where are you going?

00:19:02.519 --> 00:19:04.599
I'm going to the credit union
to get some cash

00:19:04.779 --> 00:19:06.420
so Lijun can take it back to Mr. Chen.

00:19:10.740 --> 00:19:11.519
Sir.

00:19:11.819 --> 00:19:13.539
Yes, I made an appointment.

00:19:13.779 --> 00:19:14.720
On the 10th.

00:19:14.720 --> 00:19:15.648
Six hundred thousand.

00:19:15.900 --> 00:19:17.279
It'll arrive before 1 PM.

00:19:18.680 --> 00:19:19.830
(Beiyan Shaliang Rural Credit Union)
You can send someone over

00:19:19.830 --> 00:19:21.140
to withdraw the money with me.

00:19:21.400 --> 00:19:22.740
It won't be wrong.

00:19:25.299 --> 00:19:26.144
Yes.

00:19:26.240 --> 00:19:26.940
Yes.

00:19:27.539 --> 00:19:28.819
There's no so-called...

00:19:39.059 --> 00:19:41.279
(Beiyan County Hospital)
His temperature has dropped today.

00:19:41.279 --> 00:19:42.839
- But the doctor said
- Okay.

00:19:42.940 --> 00:19:44.180
you need to hurry.

00:19:44.180 --> 00:19:44.720
Good boy.

00:19:44.720 --> 00:19:47.440
The county hospital
doesn't have the facilities for surgery.

00:19:47.480 --> 00:19:49.559
So once you've decided,

00:19:49.759 --> 00:19:51.940
we need to contact
the provincial hospital first

00:19:52.240 --> 00:19:53.559
before helping you transfer.

00:19:53.779 --> 00:19:56.559
Besides, every extra day you stay

00:19:56.680 --> 00:19:58.640
is another day
of hospital fees, isn't it?

00:19:58.980 --> 00:20:00.680
Are we deliberately staying here?

00:20:01.559 --> 00:20:04.319
What parent
wants their child to be sick?

00:20:04.440 --> 00:20:05.720
We have no choice.

00:20:05.720 --> 00:20:07.799
We want to pay the surgery fee
as soon as possible.

00:20:07.799 --> 00:20:09.500
We can't scrape it together right now.

00:20:09.680 --> 00:20:11.240
I didn't say anything.

00:20:27.552 --> 00:20:35.557
(Beiyan Shaliang Rural Credit Union)

00:20:40.700 --> 00:20:41.460
Next.

00:20:44.880 --> 00:20:45.460
Withdraw.

00:20:46.559 --> 00:20:47.259
How much?

00:20:47.420 --> 00:20:48.039
Twenty.

00:20:52.288 --> 00:20:58.085
(Beiyan Shaliang Rural Credit Union)

00:21:08.140 --> 00:21:08.960
Dazhu,

00:21:11.000 --> 00:21:12.240
we're good brothers, right?

00:21:12.880 --> 00:21:13.740
Of course, we are.

00:21:14.500 --> 00:21:16.279
Guangcai, we are the kind of brothers

00:21:16.700 --> 00:21:19.240
who go through fire and water
for each other.

00:21:22.460 --> 00:21:26.319
What if it really is fire and water
this time?

00:21:30.039 --> 00:21:31.500
What is it?

00:21:49.720 --> 00:21:50.900
There's some money.

00:21:53.660 --> 00:21:54.740
If we take it,

00:21:56.500 --> 00:21:57.740
we might risk our lives.

00:22:00.500 --> 00:22:02.839
What money? How much?

00:22:07.400 --> 00:22:08.019
Sixty thousand?

00:22:09.039 --> 00:22:09.880
Six hundred thousand.

00:22:13.880 --> 00:22:16.460
I've never seen that much money
in my life.

00:22:16.460 --> 00:22:17.460
Six hundred thousand?

00:22:22.740 --> 00:22:24.160
With that money,

00:22:25.400 --> 00:22:26.480
both Xiaoliang's illness

00:22:27.339 --> 00:22:28.500
and Mr. Chen's eyes

00:22:29.500 --> 00:22:30.496
could be taken care of.

00:22:33.779 --> 00:22:35.140
But listen to me.

00:22:36.339 --> 00:22:38.680
If I actually do it, and if...

00:22:41.900 --> 00:22:43.779
You have to help me.

00:22:45.240 --> 00:22:46.880
What is it? What will you do?

00:22:47.460 --> 00:22:48.720
Guangcai, just tell me.

00:22:49.099 --> 00:22:50.599
Whatever it is, I'll follow you.

00:23:06.740 --> 00:23:07.539
Because of me,

00:23:10.660 --> 00:23:12.500
Lijun and Dazhu

00:23:14.099 --> 00:23:15.400
agreed without any hesitation.

00:23:16.039 --> 00:23:17.480
Yonghui got dragged into that too.

00:23:22.380 --> 00:23:23.460
I'm such an idiot.

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:26.380
I'm such an idiot.

00:23:29.779 --> 00:23:31.140
Today, because of me again,

00:23:33.839 --> 00:23:35.519
they all got pulled into this mess.

00:23:42.279 --> 00:23:45.839
Aren't those you've hurt innocent?

00:23:49.500 --> 00:23:51.380
The bank clerk driven mad by the robbery

00:23:52.000 --> 00:23:54.200
and my good brothers Lin Shan
and Du Ming,

00:23:54.279 --> 00:23:55.380
what about them?

00:23:57.720 --> 00:23:59.480
And Li Fen, who bore your child.

00:24:00.220 --> 00:24:01.500
Who have you ever done right by?

00:24:14.660 --> 00:24:15.599
I have a condition.

00:24:16.599 --> 00:24:19.220
The police don't accept
any form of conditional exchange.

00:24:20.279 --> 00:24:21.839
It's effortless for you.

00:24:22.279 --> 00:24:23.140
If you agree,

00:24:26.500 --> 00:24:27.339
I'll confess.

00:24:30.839 --> 00:24:31.660
Go ahead.

00:24:42.339 --> 00:24:44.220
Forget about the stupid truth.

00:24:45.900 --> 00:24:46.680
I am

00:24:48.220 --> 00:24:49.900
Meng Xiaoliang's father.

00:24:53.660 --> 00:24:55.279
Don't tell him about his origins.

00:24:59.660 --> 00:25:01.220
I've already harmed too many people.

00:25:04.039 --> 00:25:05.519
I can't harm Xiaoliang too.

00:25:30.640 --> 00:25:31.400
Go home.

00:25:31.968 --> 00:25:33.728
The one you're waiting for
won't come out.

00:25:34.460 --> 00:25:35.599
Why hasn't he been released?

00:25:35.599 --> 00:25:36.660
Yes, Officer Zhu.

00:25:36.660 --> 00:25:37.880
Could you please tell us?

00:25:38.220 --> 00:25:39.579
Could you tell us, Officer Zhu?

00:25:40.400 --> 00:25:41.640
Why hasn't he been released?

00:25:41.640 --> 00:25:42.400
What happened?

00:25:42.400 --> 00:25:43.480
Tell us, Officer Zhu.

00:25:44.240 --> 00:25:45.079
I'm sorry.

00:25:45.079 --> 00:25:45.819
Please answer us.

00:25:45.819 --> 00:25:46.319
Officer Zhu.

00:25:46.640 --> 00:25:47.599
- Step back!
- Officer Zhu.

00:25:56.920 --> 00:25:59.480
Chief, since he's already confessed,

00:25:59.779 --> 00:26:02.140
let Officer Zhu join
the next interrogation session.

00:26:04.960 --> 00:26:06.259
Keep it steady. Go ahead.

00:26:07.000 --> 00:26:08.880
Alright, I'll go tell my master.

00:26:18.099 --> 00:26:21.180
Meng Guangcai, please describe in detail

00:26:21.380 --> 00:26:26.819
the robbery of the Beiyan Credit Union
on June 10, 1993.

00:26:34.039 --> 00:26:36.019
On June 10, 1993,

00:26:38.140 --> 00:26:42.779
a few brothers and I
robbed the Beiyan Credit Union.

00:26:43.240 --> 00:26:45.660
How many people? Who were they?

00:26:47.140 --> 00:26:48.519
Explain the details clearly.

00:26:48.819 --> 00:26:49.519
Four people.

00:26:51.519 --> 00:26:52.640
To be precise,

00:26:53.599 --> 00:26:55.460
there were four people at first.

00:26:56.160 --> 00:26:58.380
After we four arrived
at the credit union,

00:26:58.960 --> 00:27:02.839
I went in with Wang Dazhu
and Huang Mantang to get the money.

00:27:04.160 --> 00:27:06.500
Jiao Lijun kept watch outside.

00:27:23.968 --> 00:27:27.237
(Beiyan Shaliang Rural Credit Union)

00:28:06.279 --> 00:28:07.079
Don't move!

00:28:08.759 --> 00:28:09.380
Nobody move!

00:28:10.220 --> 00:28:10.920
Nobody move!

00:29:19.960 --> 00:29:20.500
Don't move!

00:29:21.339 --> 00:29:22.000
Police!

00:29:24.539 --> 00:29:25.180
Put it down!

00:29:28.240 --> 00:29:29.380
Put the gun down!

00:29:31.980 --> 00:29:32.759
Put it down!

00:29:43.500 --> 00:29:44.240
Kick it over!

00:29:47.880 --> 00:29:48.740
Kick it over!

00:29:56.579 --> 00:29:57.420
Don't move!

00:30:07.980 --> 00:30:08.680
Nobody move!

00:30:52.619 --> 00:30:53.819
Go! Go! Go!

00:30:53.819 --> 00:30:54.759
Go! Go!

00:31:00.000 --> 00:31:02.500
Xue Yonghui never intended to fire.

00:31:04.000 --> 00:31:05.000
He was young

00:31:06.240 --> 00:31:07.500
and was panicking.

00:31:09.079 --> 00:31:11.500
That homemade firearm
accidentally fired.

00:31:12.000 --> 00:31:13.960
So those involved in the robbery
that day were

00:31:14.099 --> 00:31:15.019
Jiao Lijun,

00:31:16.079 --> 00:31:16.880
Wang Dazhu,

00:31:18.000 --> 00:31:18.980
Huang Mantang,

00:31:19.680 --> 00:31:20.640
Xue Yonghui,

00:31:22.880 --> 00:31:23.599
and you.

00:31:24.240 --> 00:31:25.000
No Zuo Long?

00:31:27.460 --> 00:31:28.240
No Zuo Long.

00:31:31.000 --> 00:31:32.880
Since Zuo Long went to labor camp,

00:31:33.920 --> 00:31:35.500
we never saw him again.

00:31:36.640 --> 00:31:38.140
It had nothing to do with Zuo Long.

00:31:41.519 --> 00:31:44.000
I've told you everything I know.

00:31:45.579 --> 00:31:46.380
Officer Zhu,

00:31:47.640 --> 00:31:49.380
don't forget what you promised me.

00:31:51.319 --> 00:31:53.839
So what Jiao Lijun and Wang Dazhu
confessed earlier

00:31:54.740 --> 00:31:56.460
was all prearranged by you, right?

00:31:58.640 --> 00:31:59.579
We had no choice.

00:32:01.500 --> 00:32:02.500
It's been 18 years.

00:32:04.140 --> 00:32:05.759
You won't let me go.

00:32:08.819 --> 00:32:10.740
The more Caisheng Group grows,

00:32:10.740 --> 00:32:11.839
the more worried

00:32:13.259 --> 00:32:14.500
I become.

00:32:17.240 --> 00:32:20.319
I planned all of that.

00:32:20.640 --> 00:32:23.920
The others were just
playing along with me.

00:32:26.240 --> 00:32:27.640
They played their parts well.

00:32:40.279 --> 00:32:41.599
Isn't this moment

00:32:43.740 --> 00:32:45.299
exactly what you wanted to see?

00:32:48.500 --> 00:32:51.240
What else do you want to know
about the robbery?

00:32:52.420 --> 00:32:53.579
I'll cooperate fully.

00:32:56.380 --> 00:32:57.380
All these years,

00:33:00.400 --> 00:33:02.400
I've always believed
you committed the crime.

00:33:03.759 --> 00:33:04.920
But for all these years,

00:33:07.539 --> 00:33:09.039
I couldn't bring myself to believe

00:33:12.539 --> 00:33:14.160
that Meng Guangcai, the brother

00:33:17.079 --> 00:33:19.140
I've known so long and so well, did it.

00:33:23.380 --> 00:33:25.039
I guess people change.

00:33:32.500 --> 00:33:33.160
Zhu,

00:33:35.680 --> 00:33:37.380
from the year we met,

00:33:38.740 --> 00:33:39.720
you and I

00:33:41.799 --> 00:33:42.980
haven't really changed.

00:33:45.380 --> 00:33:46.160
Don't you agree?

00:34:36.480 --> 00:34:37.460
Zhu?

00:34:42.260 --> 00:34:43.300
What brings you here?

00:34:51.539 --> 00:34:52.380
Zhu, why

00:34:54.159 --> 00:34:55.579
are you looking at me like that?

00:35:13.719 --> 00:35:14.460
Zhu,

00:35:18.260 --> 00:35:19.099
I know

00:35:23.440 --> 00:35:24.420
I've committed a crime.

00:35:30.460 --> 00:35:31.320
But Zhu,

00:35:32.159 --> 00:35:33.539
I didn't want to do that.

00:35:34.219 --> 00:35:36.760
I just wanted a quiet life with Qin.

00:35:36.760 --> 00:35:39.500
I wanted to learn
how to be a good man from you.

00:35:40.300 --> 00:35:41.639
Can you let me go?

00:35:41.920 --> 00:35:43.460
Zhu, can you let me go?

00:35:44.000 --> 00:35:46.599
I'm begging you, let me go.

00:35:47.360 --> 00:35:48.820
Please, Zhu.